    "Firstly, we left the LLM analyze the entire case and highlight key findings.",
    "Successively, we investigated about the model's ability to provide coherent surgical choices, writing the question \"What kind of surgery would you perform?\"",
    "(Figs. 1 and 2).",
    "In some instances, when the answers were overly generalist, we asked the model for further explanations regarding the treatment of choice, based on the specific conditions of the clinical case, asking the chatbots to choose only one treatment.",
